Description: Microphone noise cancellation and monitor mode
 SoftNoise applies real-time noise cancellation to your microphone
 using the RNNoise neural network model. It supports monitor mode
 (sidetone) so you can hear your cleaned audio through headphones,
 and provides system-wide NC instructions via a PipeWire virtual sink.
